OL,3,CEver been totally gazeboed? Linguists
OL,4,Cfind 546 'drunkonyms' in English
OL,5,Clanguage
OL,7,FBy Lily Ford, ITV News Multimedia
OL,8,FProducer
OL,10,FHave you ever been utterly gazeboed
OL,11,Fafter one too many glasses of wine?
OL,13,FYou also might have been carparked,
OL,14,Ftrollied, or even pyjamaed, it turns
OL,15,Fout, after two German linguists took
OL,16,Fthe claim of British comedian very
OL,17,Fseriously.
