OL,7,FEven though excessive alcohol
OL,8,Fconsumption may come with negative
OL,9,Fconsequences, drunkenness is commonly
OL,10,Fdiscussed using a wide range of light-
OL,11,Fhearted linguistic means in English,
OL,12,Fthe study also found.
OL,14,FProfessor Sanchez-Stockhammer
OL,15,Fobserved: "The humorous effect of
OL,16,Fdrunkonyms is often achieved through
OL,17,Ftheir indirectness."
